            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": true,
            "last_activity_date": 1292413494,
            "creation_date": 1292413494,
            "body": "<p>I suggest you try either DecimalFormat, or String.format or PrintStream.printf depending on what is most appropriate for you. I also suggest you try to accept more answers. ;)<\/p>\n",
